title: I Am Not Your Milkshake - Novel Updates
tags: Broken Engagement   Character Growth   Comedic Undertone   Debts   Female Protagonist
author: 小包子
description:
After the overnight bankruptcy, her grandfather ran away and her friends avoided her as much as possible. She was left all alone to deal with the flood of creditors.

Worse still, she was driven out in an interview and could only live on convenient noodles.

Facing her biggest creditor, she held his thigh firmly and said in a coquettish way.>
